These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, photographer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
2 different games are played: poker, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the photographer is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Job   | photographer     | electrician   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Game     | poker | billiard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, basketball
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, tiparillo
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Sport           | basketball         | climbing     |
| Cigar     | bluemaster   | tiparillo    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
