The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, ice-hockey
2 different games are played: poker, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Sport         | snowboarding         | ice-hockey        |
| Game   | poker         | billiard    |

