.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
House: wooden, farmhouse
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, november
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the farmhouse house is the dutch##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| House           | farmhouse | wooden    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Birthday           | january         | november    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

