There are 2 different nationalities: australian, indian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the indian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Nationality         | indian        | australian |
| Birthday         | march          | december     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 